#. metadata.json->name
msgid "Google Drive"
msgstr "Google Drive"

#. metadata.json->description
msgid ""
"A simple applet to be able to sync Google Drive folders and files with just "
"a few clicks."
msgstr ""
"Een eenvoudige applet om Google Drive-mappen en -bestanden te synchroniseren "
"met slechts een paar klikken."

#. settings-schema.json->pageConfiguration->title
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Configuratie"

#. settings-schema.json->pageHelp->title
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Hulp"

#. settings-schema.json->sectionGeneralOptions->title
msgid "Google Drive Options"
msgstr "Google Drive-opties"

#. settings-schema.json->sectionRcloneConfig->title
msgid "rclone Remote"
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->sectionWhitelist->title
msgid "Whitelisted Folders"
msgstr "Whitelist Mappen"

#. settings-schema.json->sectionRcloneDocs->title
msgid "rclone Setup"
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->sectionHelp->title
msgid "About/Help"
msgstr "Over/Hulp"

#. settings-schema.json->sectionIssues->title
msgid "Bugs/Issues"
msgstr "Fouten/Problemen"

#. settings-schema.json->location->description
msgid "Drive Sync Location"
msgstr "Drive Synchronisatielocatie"

#. settings-schema.json->location->tooltip
msgid ""
"Location to an empty folder where it will sync the Google Drive data to e.g. "
"~/Documents/Drive."
msgstr ""
"Locatie naar een lege map waar de Google Drive-gegevens naartoe worden "
"gesynchroniseerd, bijv. ~/Documenten/Drive."

#. settings-schema.json->remote->description
msgid "rclone Remote Name"
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->remote->tooltip
msgid ""
"The name of your rclone Google Drive remote, without the trailing colon (e."
"g. gdrive). Run 'rclone listremotes' in a terminal to see your configured "
"remotes."
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->remoteHelp->description
msgid ""
"Enter the rclone remote name configured for Google Drive (run 'rclone "
"listremotes' in a terminal to see your remotes, without the trailing colon e."
"g. gdrive)."
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->whitelistHelp->description
msgid ""
"Note: If you want to sync only specific folders please make sure to add them "
"on the list above. Please enter the names exactly as they are named in your "
"Drive! It is also possible to add subfolders e.g. Documents/Work/Projects."
msgstr ""
"Opmerking: Als u alleen specifieke mappen wilt synchroniseren, zorg er dan "
"voor dat u ze toevoegt aan de bovenstaande lijst. Voer de namen exact in "
"zoals ze genoemd in uw Drive zijn! Het is ook mogelijk om submappen toe te "
"voegen, bijv. Documenten/Werk/Projecten."

#. settings-schema.json->whitelist->columns->title
msgid "Folder Name"
msgstr "Mapnaam"

#. settings-schema.json->whitelist->description
msgid "Whitelist Folders"
msgstr "Whitelist Mappen"

#. settings-schema.json->whitelist->tooltip
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Whitelist folders that will be synced from Google Drive e.g. Documents, "
"Photos"
msgstr ""
"Whitelist mappen die zullen worden gesynchroniseerd vanuit Google Drive, "
"bijv. Documenten, Foto's"

#. settings-schema.json->rcloneDocs->description
msgid ""
"To configure rclone with Google Drive, click the button below to open the "
"official rclone Google Drive documentation."
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->rcloneDocsButton->description
#, fuzzy
msgid "Open rclone Google Drive Docs"
msgstr "Google Drive-opties"

#. settings-schema.json->rcloneDocsButton->tooltip
msgid "Opens the rclone Google Drive setup documentation in a browser."
msgstr ""

#. settings-schema.json->website->description
msgid ""
"To learn more about the applet please click the button below to visit the "
"official repository for this applet."
msgstr ""
"Om meer te weten te komen over de applet, klik op de knop hieronder om de "
"officiële repository voor deze applet te bezoeken."

#. settings-schema.json->websiteButton->description
msgid "Visit GitHub website"
msgstr "Bezoek GitHub-website"

#. settings-schema.json->websiteButton->tooltip
msgid "Opens GitHub website to learn more about this applet."
msgstr "Opent de GitHub-website om meer te weten te komen over deze applet."

#. settings-schema.json->helpAbout->description
msgid ""
"To learn more about the applet please click the button below to visit the "
"official Cinnamon Spices website for this applet. You can also leave "
"feedback in the comment section below."
msgstr ""
"Om meer te weten te komen over de applet, klik op de knop hieronder om de "
"officiële Cinnamon Spices-website voor deze applet te bezoeken. U kunt ook "
"feedback achterlaten in de opmerkingensectie hieronder."

#. settings-schema.json->helpAboutButton->description
msgid "Visit Cinnamon Spices website"
msgstr "Bezoek Cinnamon Spices-website"

#. settings-schema.json->helpAboutButton->tooltip
msgid "Opens Cinnamon Spices website to learn more about this applet."
msgstr ""
"Opent de Cinnamon Spices-website om meer te weten te komen over deze applet."

#. settings-schema.json->helpIssue->description
msgid ""
"If you find an issue with this applet please make a report on GitHub by "
"clicking the button below. Please make sure that the issue doesn't already "
"exists"
msgstr ""
"Als u een probleem met deze applet vindt, maak dan een melding op GitHub "
"door op de onderstaande knop te klikken. Zorg ervoor dat het probleem nog "
"niet bestaat."

#. settings-schema.json->helpSubmitIssue->description
msgid "Submit an Issue"
msgstr "Meld een probleem"

#. settings-schema.json->helpSubmitIssue->tooltip
msgid ""
"Opens GitHub project page where you can submit a new issue for this applet."
msgstr ""
"Opent de GitHub-projectpagina waar u een nieuw probleem voor deze applet "
"kunt indienen."
